问员接着一个审问员，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"4ed7f7043b","type":"paragraph","text":"在我面前","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"f064bb8b07","type":"paragraph","text":"忙啊！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"84eddb80b4","type":"paragraph","text":"忙啊！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"a782664f48","type":"paragraph","text":"我爱的审问员呀！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"af45fd9f9e","type":"paragraph","text":"我恨的审问员呀！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"e91162af2c","type":"paragraph","text":"我健壮，没关系，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"25befcea5b","type":"paragraph","text":"我只怨你审问太轻率，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"afadbb15b5","type":"paragraph","text":"随随便便逮捕，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"70487c33ce","type":"paragraph","text":"随随便便定罪，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"4f936c2cf9","type":"paragraph","text":"随随便便释放。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"cc05dcf1e9","type":"paragraph","text":"×××　　×××","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"2dad7de1f7","type":"paragraph","text":"前年九月里的一天，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"5b643af35d","type":"paragraph","text":"我又被押到很多人面前。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"750a19d9a2","type":"paragraph","text":"他们","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"be409d9728","type":"paragraph","text":"狂怒！","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"bad0e05433","type":"paragraph","text":"咆哮！","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"6201036bd9","type":"paragraph","text":"高呼！","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"43b0f8c8af","type":"paragraph","text":"“………”","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"a0532d6cd7","type":"paragraph","text":"一个人接着一个人，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"22d33dcf70","type":"paragraph","text":"一个突击队接着一个突击队。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"837c84e205","type":"paragraph","text":"在我的眼前","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"efa999b4f7","type":"paragraph","text":"转呀！","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"b509e6003c","type":"paragraph","text":"转呀！","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"b37e8dbd05","type":"paragraph","text":"我多难过啊！","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"18495eff03","type":"paragraph","text":"——是前世做了什么孽，无罪受冤。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"90b8772897","type":"paragraph","text":"我多感动啊！","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"a182ab43a6","type":"paragraph","text":"——他们要坚决、澈底、到底，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"80e6ebcd27","type":"paragraph","text":"——他们显得忠诚、勇敢。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"b9c2fd0d67","type":"paragraph","text":"×××　　×××","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"92c16800a2","type":"paragraph","text":"今年，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"cdaa65535d","type":"paragraph","text":"我再碰不到审问员，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"549c930d10","type":"paragraph","text":"也再没被押到很多人面前。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"e2fc9f0418","type":"paragraph","text":"只遇到很多人，他们与我","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"ca1b54e2e4","type":"paragraph","text":"点点头，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"d5acc335b9","type":"paragraph","text":"瞪瞪眼，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"c708644768","type":"paragraph","text":"互不睬理……","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"86866d2481","type":"paragraph","text":"一个人接着一个人，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"199d5b2f29","type":"paragraph","text":"一个领导接着一个领导","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"19f9ecc856","type":"paragraph","text":"在我面前","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"0514fbd4e6","type":"paragraph","text":"过去","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"f921b82f97","type":"paragraph","text":"过去","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"4a2f06c906","type":"paragraph","text":"我多难受啊！","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"6152e14dfb","type":"paragraph","text":"——他们还有什么理由让我孤独？","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"78ae39b827","type":"paragraph","text":"我多感慨啊！","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"d97a3d3b30","type":"paragraph","text":"他们为什么不再审问？","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"3317c55ef4","type":"paragraph","text":"他们为什么不再坚决、澈底、到底","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"},{"id":"16008b1958","type":"paragraph","text":"他们为什么要赶走这颗赶不走的共产主义赤心。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8"}],"page":{"id":"be0d614830","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e70c67a3d8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}